           <p>
            Check out photos from the 2018 Mining Engineering Awards Banquet!
           </p>
          </li>
          <li>
           <h3>
            <a href="https://mail-attachment.googleusercontent.com/attachment/u/0/?ui=2&amp;ik=b943d9b9bb&amp;view=att&amp;th=16346ecd3e37d1f3&amp;attid=0.3&amp;disp=inline&amp;safe=1&amp;zw&amp;saddbat=ANGjdJ_V5vZVynhugE5-Ia0N7qjlG1aflCRXiZTwL1TicRdiJJvyOushNUpUmXZDa-y0bJaSxmuoqWBzobgpGKPLxA-XXDC3mg-IYweaSdM7oFKeWQfVsK2NokIG6fsi-LqIaUIrW458Z0gam7i_vUnoPP5oe6-NmhJB7g3FXUg45ByJ7jsXgtfcpsflO2Yjk4nWQ50fGuMaP3sWHTGDCIytiy-IOKPeSsjRSU-mYY2aV-5NFgShf-mRrWHlwyMmFtat0erE4JV3vGcqRm6d9vDXQhZkow1QccGt0ta1KUcA1tpsDf9aNZBE56fpbj-Hv9kmvXj6vp_kfnM0gdTSavnrlXEEcSrXWBMX6BNddX">
             Awards Announced at the Mining Engineering annual banquet
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p>
            See all the award winners at the 2018 Mining Engineering Banquet
           </p>
          </li>
          <li>
           <h3>
            <a href="https://www.mining.utah.edu/news/john_e_nelson_award_2018.php">
             John E. Wilson Distinguished Alumnus Award to Dr. Michael K. McCarter
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p>
            The John E. Willson Distinguished Alumnus Award
was established in 2000 to recognize graduates of the
University of Utah’s Mining Engineering Program who
have set high standards by their professional
accomplishments and service to the mining industry.
The 2018 John E. Willson Distinguished Alumnus is
Dr. Michael K. McCarter. Kim graduated Magna Cum
Laude with a B.S. in 1965 and Ph.D. in 1972 both in
Mining Engineering.
           </p>
          </li>
          <li>
           <h3>
            <a href="https://www.mining.utah.edu/news/Howard_W_Eavenson_2018.php">
             Howard W. Eavenson Award to Michael G. Nelson
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p>
            The Howard W. Eavenson Award is presented to Michael G. Nelson "for his contributions to coal mining and processing, in mining machine automation, mine ventilation, ground control, and mine health and safety.
           </p>
          </li>
         </ul>
